{"number":3,"verseCount":27,"verses":[[1,["And again my brethren, I would call your attention, for I have somewhat more to speak unto you; for behold, I have things to tell you concerning that which is to come."]],[2,["And the things which I shall tell you are made known unto me by an ",["angel",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mosiah 4:1","bofm/mosiah/4.1"],"; ",["5:5","bofm/mosiah/5.5"],". ",["TG Angels","tg/angels"],"."]]]," from God. And he said unto me: ",["Awake",["study-note-ref","b",[["Zech. 4:1 (1–2)","ot/zech/4.1-2"],"."]]],"; and I awoke, and behold he stood before me."]],[3,["And he said unto me: Awake, and hear the words which I shall tell thee; for behold, I am come to declare unto you the ",["glad",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 52:7 (7–10)","ot/isa/52.7-10"],"; ",["Luke 2:10 (10–11)","nt/luke/2.10-11"],"; ",["Rom. 10:15","nt/rom/10.15"],"; ",["D&C 31:3","dc-testament/dc/31.3"],"."]]]," tidings of great ",["joy",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]],"."]],[4,["For the Lord hath heard thy prayers, and hath judged of thy ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],", and hath sent me to declare unto thee that thou mayest rejoice; and that thou mayest declare unto thy people, that they may also be filled with joy."]],[5,["For behold, the time cometh, and is not far distant, that with power, the ",["Lord",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah","tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"],"."]]]," ",["Omnipotent",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rev. 1:8 (7–8)","nt/rev/1.7-8"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Power of","tg/jesus-christ-power-of"],"."]]]," who ",["reigneth",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"."]]],", who was, and is from all ",["eternity",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Ne. 26:12","bofm/2-ne/26.12"],"; ",["Mosiah 16:15","bofm/mosiah/16.15"],"."]]]," to all eternity, shall come down from heaven among the ",["",152],"children of men, and shall dwell in a ",["tabernacle",["study-note-ref","e",[["Mosiah 7:27","bofm/mosiah/7.27"],"; ",["15:2 (1–7)","bofm/mosiah/15.1-7"],"; ",["Alma 7:9 (9–13)","bofm/alma/7.9-13"],"."]]]," of clay, and shall go forth amongst men, working mighty ",["miracles",["study-note-ref","f",[["Matt. 4:24 (23–24)","nt/matt/4.23-24"],"; ",["9:35","nt/matt/9.35"],"; ",["Acts 2:22","nt/acts/2.22"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:31","bofm/1-ne/11.31"],". ",["TG Death, Power over","tg/death-power-over"],"; ",["Heal","tg/heal"],"; ",["Miracle","tg/miracle"],"."]]],", such as healing the sick, raising the dead, causing the lame to walk, the ",["blind",["study-note-ref","g",[["Matt. 9:28 (28–31)","nt/matt/9.28-31"],"; ",["20:30 (30–34)","nt/matt/20.30-34"],"; ",["John 9:1 (1–4)","nt/john/9.1-4"],"; ",["3 Ne. 17:9 (7–10)","bofm/3-ne/17.7-10"],"; ",["D&C 84:69","dc-testament/dc/84.69"],"."]]]," to receive their sight, and the deaf to hear, and curing all manner of diseases."]],[6,["And he shall cast out ",["devils",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mark 1:34 (32–34)","nt/mark/1.32-34"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:31","bofm/1-ne/11.31"],"."]]],", or the ",["evil spirits",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean","tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"],"."]]]," which dwell in the hearts of the children of men."]],[7,["And lo, he shall ",["suffer",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 12:50","nt/luke/12.50"],". ",["TG Suffering","tg/suffering"],"."]]]," ",["temptations",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Temptation of","tg/jesus-christ-temptation-of"],"; ",["Temptation","tg/temptation"],"."]]],", and pain of body, ",["hunger",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 4:2 (1–2)","nt/matt/4.1-2"],"."]]],", thirst, and fatigue, even more than man can ",["suffer",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 19:16 (15–18)","dc-testament/dc/19.15-18"],"."]]],", except it be unto death; for behold, ",["blood",["study-note-ref","e",[["Matt. 26:39 (38–39)","nt/matt/26.38-39"],"; ",["Luke 22:44","nt/luke/22.44"],"."]]]," cometh from every pore, so great shall be his ",["anguish",["study-note-ref","f",[["Isa. 53:4 (4–5)","ot/isa/53.4-5"],"."]]]," for the wickedness and the abominations of his people."]],[8,["And he shall be called ",["Jesus",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Foreordination","tg/foreordination"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Prophecies about","tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"],"."]]]," ",["Christ",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messiah","tg/jesus-christ-messiah"],"."]]],", the ",["Son of God",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mosiah 15:3","bofm/mosiah/15.3"],"; ",["Alma 7:10","bofm/alma/7.10"],"; ",["3 Ne. 1:14","bofm/3-ne/1.14"],"."]]],", the ",["Father",["study-note-ref","d",[["Mosiah 15:4","bofm/mosiah/15.4"],"; ",["Hel. 14:12","bofm/hel/14.12"],"; ",["3 Ne. 9:15","bofm/3-ne/9.15"],"; ",["Ether 4:7","bofm/ether/4.7"],"."]]]," of heaven and earth, the ",["Creator",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Creator","tg/jesus-christ-creator"],"."]]]," of all things from the beginning; and his ",["mother",["study-note-ref","f",[["Matt. 1:16","nt/matt/1.16"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:18 (14–21)","bofm/1-ne/11.14-21"],"."]]]," shall be called Mary."]],[9,["And lo, he cometh unto his own, that ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"."]]]," might come unto the children of men even through ",["faith",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," on his name; and even after all this they shall consider him a man, and say that he hath a ",["devil",["study-note-ref","c",[["Luke 11:15 (14–22)","nt/luke/11.14-22"],"; ",["John 8:48","nt/john/8.48"],"; ",["12:37","nt/john/12.37"],"; ",["Hel. 13:26 (26–27)","bofm/hel/13.26-27"],"."]]],", and shall ",["scourge",["study-note-ref","d",[["Luke 18:33","nt/luke/18.33"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:33","bofm/1-ne/11.33"],"; ",["2 Ne. 10:3","bofm/2-ne/10.3"],"."]]]," him, and shall ",["crucify",["study-note-ref","e",[["1 Ne. 19:10 (10, 13)","bofm/1-ne/19.10,13"],"; ",["2 Ne. 6:9","bofm/2-ne/6.9"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:14 (14–15, 33)","bofm/3-ne/11.14-15,33"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of","tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"],"."]]]," him."]],[10,["And he shall ",["rise",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection","tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"],"."]]]," the ",["third",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 25:13","bofm/2-ne/25.13"],"; ",["Hel. 14:20 (20–27)","bofm/hel/14.20-27"],"."]]]," day from the dead; and behold, he standeth to ",["judge",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Judge","tg/jesus-christ-judge"],"."]]]," the world; and behold, all these things are done that a righteous judgment might come upon the children of men."]],[11,["For behold, and also his ",["blood",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Blood, Symbolism of","tg/blood-symbolism-of"],"."]]]," ",["atoneth",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"; ",["Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]]," for the sins of those who have ",["fallen",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Fall of Man","tg/fall-of-man"],"."]]]," by the transgression of Adam, who have died not knowing the ",["will",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God, Will of","tg/god-will-of"],"."]]]," of God concerning them, or who have ",["ignorantly",["study-note-ref","e",[["Lev. 4:13 (13–35)","ot/lev/4.13-35"],"; ",["Num. 15:27 (2–29)","ot/num/15.2-29"],"; ",["2 Ne. 9:26 (25–26)","bofm/2-ne/9.25-26"],"; ",["Alma 9:16 (15–16)","bofm/alma/9.15-16"],"; ",["42:21","bofm/alma/42.21"],"; ",["3 Ne. 6:18","bofm/3-ne/6.18"],". ",["TG Accountability","tg/accountability"],"; ",["Ignorance","tg/ignorance"],"."]]]," sinned."]],[12,["But wo, wo unto him who knoweth that he ",["rebelleth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mosiah 2:37 (36–38)","bofm/mosiah/2.36-38"],"; ",["Hel. 8:25 (24–25)","bofm/hel/8.24-25"],". ",["TG Rebellion","tg/rebellion"],"."]]]," against God! For salvation cometh to none such except it be through repentance and faith on the ",["Lord Jesus Christ",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Lord","tg/jesus-christ-lord"],"."]]],"."]],[13,["And the Lord God hath sent his holy ",["prophets",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prophets, Mission of","tg/prophets-mission-of"],"."]]]," among all the children of men, to declare these things to every kindred, nation, and tongue, that thereby whosoever should believe that Christ should come, the same might receive ",["remission",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]]," of their sins, and rejoice with exceedingly great joy, even ",["as",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 25:26 (24–27)","bofm/2-ne/25.24-27"],"; ",["Jarom 1:11","bofm/jarom/1.11"],"; ",["Mosiah 16:6","bofm/mosiah/16.6"],"."]]]," though he had already come among them."]],[14,["Yet the Lord God saw that his people were a ",["stiffnecked",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 25:28","bofm/2-ne/25.28"],"; ",["Alma 9:31","bofm/alma/9.31"],". ",["TG Stiffnecked","tg/stiffnecked"],"."]]]," people, and he appointed unto them a ",["law",["study-note-ref","b",[["Josh. 1:8","ot/josh/1.8"],"; ",["Mosiah 13:29 (29–32)","bofm/mosiah/13.29-32"],"; ",["Alma 25:15 (15–16)","bofm/alma/25.15-16"],"; ",["D&C 41:5 (4–5)","dc-testament/dc/41.4-5"],"."]]],", even the ",["law",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]]," of Moses."]],[15,["And many signs, and wonders, and ",["types",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation","tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"],"; ",["Passover","tg/passover"],"; ",["Symbolism","tg/symbolism"],"."]]],", and shadows showed he unto them, concerning his coming; and also holy prophets spake unto them concerning his coming; and yet they ",["hardened",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Hardheartedness","tg/hardheartedness"],"."]]]," their hearts, and understood not that the ",["law",["study-note-ref","c",[["Heb. 10:1","nt/heb/10.1"],"; ",["Mosiah 12:31","bofm/mosiah/12.31"],"; ",["13:28 (27–32)","bofm/mosiah/13.27-32"],"; ",["Alma 25:16","bofm/alma/25.16"],"."]]]," of Moses availeth nothing ",["except",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Ne. 11:6","bofm/2-ne/11.6"],"."]]]," it were through the ",["atonement",["study-note-ref","e",[["Lev. 4:20","ot/lev/4.20"],"; ",["Matt. 26:54 (51–56)","nt/matt/26.51-56"],"."]]]," of his blood."]],[16,["And even if it were possible that little ",["children",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Conceived in Sin","tg/conceived-in-sin"],"."]]]," could sin they could not be saved; but I say unto you they are ",["blessed",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Salvation of Little Children","tg/salvation-of-little-children"],"."]]],"; for behold, as in Adam, or by nature, they fall, even so the blood of Christ ",["atoneth",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moro. 8:8 (8–9)","bofm/moro/8.8-9"],"; ",["Moses 6:54 (54–56)","pgp/moses/6.54-56"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]]," for their sins."]],[17,["And moreover, I say unto you, that there shall be ",["no",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 4:12 (10–12)","nt/acts/4.10-12"],"; ",["2 Ne. 31:21","bofm/2-ne/31.21"],"; ",["Mosiah 4:8 (7–8)","bofm/mosiah/4.7-8"],"; ",["3 Ne. 9:17","bofm/3-ne/9.17"],"."]]]," other name given nor any other way nor means whereby ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 7:14 (13–14)","nt/matt/7.13-14"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Savior","tg/jesus-christ-savior"],"; ",["Salvation, Plan of","tg/salvation-plan-of"],"."]]]," can come unto the children of men, only in and through the name of Christ, the ",["Lord",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Lord","tg/jesus-christ-lord"],"."]]]," Omnipotent."]],[18,["For behold he judgeth, and his judgment is just; and the infant perisheth not that dieth in his infancy; but men drink ",["damnation",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Cor. 11:29","nt/1-cor/11.29"],"."]]]," to their own souls except they humble themselves and ",["become",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 18:3","nt/matt/18.3"],"."]]]," as little children, and believe that ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]]," was, and is, and is to come, in and through the ",["atoning",["study-note-ref","d",[["Mosiah 4:2","bofm/mosiah/4.2"],"; ",["Hel. 5:9","bofm/hel/5.9"],"."]]]," blood of Christ, the Lord Omnipotent."]],[19,["For the ",["natural",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gen. 8:21","ot/gen/8.21"],"; ",["1 Cor. 2:14 (11–14)","nt/1-cor/2.11-14"],"; ",["2 Pet. 2:12","nt/2-pet/2.12"],"; ",["Mosiah 16:3","bofm/mosiah/16.3"],"; ",["Alma 41:11","bofm/alma/41.11"],"; ",["Ether 3:2","bofm/ether/3.2"],". ",["TG Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn","tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"],"; ",["Worldliness","tg/worldliness"],"."]]]," ",["man",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Mortality","tg/mortality"],"."]]]," is an ",["enemy",["study-note-ref","c",[["James 4:4","nt/james/4.4"],". ",["TG Enemies","tg/enemies"],"."]]]," to God, and has been from the ",["fall",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Fall of Man","tg/fall-of-man"],"."]]]," of Adam, and will be, forever and ever, unless he ",["yields",["study-note-ref","e",[["2 Chr. 30:8","ot/2-chr/30.8"],"; ",["Rom. 6:13 (12–14)","nt/rom/6.12-14"],"."]]]," to the enticings of the ",["Holy Spirit",["study-note-ref","f",[["Rom. 8:4 (1–9)","nt/rom/8.1-9"],". ",["TG Guidance, Divine","tg/guidance-divine"],"."]]],", and ",["putteth",["study-note-ref","g",[["Alma 19:6","bofm/alma/19.6"],"."]]]," off the ",["natural",["study-note-ref","h",[["Col. 3:9","nt/col/3.9"],"; ",["D&C 67:12","dc-testament/dc/67.12"],"."]]]," man and becometh a ",["saint",["study-note-ref","i",[["Luke 22:32 (31–38)","nt/luke/22.31-38"],". ",["TG Man, New, Spiritually Reborn","tg/man-new-spiritually-reborn"],"; ",["Saints","tg/saints"],"; ",["Spirituality","tg/spirituality"],"."]]]," through the atonement of Christ the Lord, and becometh as a ",["child",["study-note-ref","j",[["Matt. 18:3","nt/matt/18.3"],"; ",["1 Pet. 2:2 (1–3)","nt/1-pet/2.1-3"],"; ",["3 Ne. 9:22","bofm/3-ne/9.22"],"."]]],", ",["submissive",["study-note-ref","k",[["TG Self-Mastery","tg/self-mastery"],"; ",["Submissiveness","tg/submissiveness"],"."]]],", meek, humble, patient, full of love, willing to submit to all things which the Lord seeth fit to inflict upon him, even as a child doth submit to his father."]],[20,["And moreover, I say unto you, that the time shall come when the ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 3:16","dc-testament/dc/3.16"],"."]]]," of a ",["Savior",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Savior","tg/jesus-christ-savior"],"."]]]," shall spread throughout ",["every",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mosiah 16:1","bofm/mosiah/16.1"],". ",["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"."]]]," nation, kindred, tongue, and people."]],[21,["And behold, when that time cometh, none shall be found ",["blameless",["study-note-ref","a",[["Col. 1:22","nt/col/1.22"],"; ",["D&C 4:2","dc-testament/dc/4.2"],". ",["TG Accountability","tg/accountability"],"."]]]," before God, except it be little children, only through repentance and faith on the name of the Lord God Omnipotent."]],[22,["And even at this time, when thou shalt have taught thy people the things which the Lord thy God hath commanded thee, even then ",["",154],"are they found no more blameless in the sight of God, only according to the words which I have spoken unto thee."]],[23,["And now I have spoken the words which the Lord God hath commanded me."]],[24,["And thus saith the Lord: They shall stand as a bright testimony against this people, at the judgment day; whereof they shall be judged, every man according to his ",["works",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Good Works","tg/good-works"],"."]]],", whether they be good, or whether they be evil."]],[25,["And if they be evil they are consigned to an awful ",["view",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 9:14, 46","bofm/2-ne/9.14,46"],"; ",["Alma 5:18","bofm/alma/5.18"],"; ",["11:43","bofm/alma/11.43"],"; ",["12:15 (14–15)","bofm/alma/12.14-15"],"."]]]," of their own guilt and abominations, which doth cause them to shrink from the presence of the Lord into a state of ",["misery",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 3:16","nt/rom/3.16"],"; ",["Morm. 8:38","bofm/morm/8.38"],"."]]]," and ",["endless",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Punish","tg/punish"],"."]]]," torment, from whence they can no more return; therefore they have drunk damnation to their own souls."]],[26,["Therefore, they have drunk out of the ",["cup",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 75:8","ot/ps/75.8"],"; ",["Jer. 25:15","ot/jer/25.15"],"; ",["Lam. 4:21","ot/lam/4.21"],"."]]]," of the wrath of God, which justice could no more deny unto them than it could deny that ",["Adam",["study-note-ref","b",[["Morm. 9:12","bofm/morm/9.12"],"; ",["Moro. 8:8","bofm/moro/8.8"],"."]]]," should fall because of his partaking of the forbidden ",["fruit",["study-note-ref","c",[["Gen. 3:6","ot/gen/3.6"],"; ",["2 Ne. 2:15 (15–19)","bofm/2-ne/2.15-19"],"; ",["Alma 12:22 (21–23)","bofm/alma/12.21-23"],"."]]],"; therefore, ",["mercy",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Mercy","tg/mercy"],"."]]]," could have claim on them no more forever."]],[27,["And their ",["torment",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Hell","tg/hell"],"."]]]," is as a ",["lake",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 9:16","bofm/2-ne/9.16"],"; ",["Jacob 6:10","bofm/jacob/6.10"],"; ",["Alma 12:17","bofm/alma/12.17"],"; ",["D&C 76:36","dc-testament/dc/76.36"],"."]]]," of fire and brimstone, whose flames are unquenchable, and whose smoke ascendeth up ",["forever",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mosiah 5:5","bofm/mosiah/5.5"],"."]]]," and ever. Thus hath the Lord commanded me. Amen."]]],"volume":"bm"}